primarys.simple_primary:
"

This example tests the implementation of Buildings.Fluid.HeatExchangers.ActiveBeams.CoolingAndHeating for both heating and cooling mode. An air volume is maintained at a temperature between 22ˆC and 25ˆC by two controllers that regulate the water flow rate in the active beam.

"
